# Execution Layer visual freeze (Why GenZrix)

**Naming:** User-facing "Execution Layer" = homepage **Why GenZrix** section (`about-why-section.why-genzrix`). This is **not** the Services Showcase carousel (`initServicesShowcase` / `services-showcase.html`).

**Status:** Visual design is **locked** (June 2026). Summary stack (`.is-compact`) is the reference implementation.

## Do not modify (visual)

Unless the user explicitly requests a visual redesign:

- Active / inactive stacked card appearance, glassmorphism, metal surfaces
- Border radius, shadows, blur, background gradients, card dimensions
- Stack depth, card offsets, spacing, layout grid (logo | headline | stack)
- Icon styling: static dark navy gradient `#2E4058 → #20222C`, accent icon color `var(--ds-accent)`
- Typography: heading sizes, description styling, left badge/ring, headline
- Summary morph / compact row styling (`.is-compact`, `.is-morph-layout`)
- Responsive breakpoints for this section
- CSS transitions on colors, backgrounds, shadows, glass effects in this section

## Allowed changes (functional only)

- Scroll progression, pacing, thresholds, pin distance in `initWhyGenzrixStack()`
- Transform / opacity / z-index driven per frame by scroll (not CSS color transitions)
- Content text updates in `index.html` (copy only — no markup/class changes)
- Bug fixes that restore the frozen baseline (not redesign)

## Key files & selectors

| Asset | Location |
|-------|----------|
| Markup | `index.html` — `[data-why-stack-scroll]`, `[data-why-stack]`, `[data-why-card]` |
| Visual CSS | `style.css` — `.why-genzrix-*`, `.ds-section--about .why-genzrix-*`, `.why-genzrix-stack-card.is-compact` |
| Interaction JS | `script.js` — `initWhyGenzrixStack()` (logic only; no new inline visual styles) |

## When visual change is unavoidable

1. Match existing summary stack (`.is-compact`) tokens: `--metal-*`, `--surface-*`, icon gradient above
2. Change the smallest possible rule; do not refactor unrelated styles
3. State explicitly that the user approved a visual exception
